{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-case-study-template-js","path":"/visualactivities/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"lucid-softwares-visual-activities\">Lucid Software's Visual Activities</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Building a collaborative, on-canvas survey tool for Lucid users.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/c841b/hero.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 27.999999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset='/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/c85cb/hero.webp 300w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/e88ff/hero.webp 600w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/92f8c/hero.webp 1200w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/62ed8/hero.webp 1800w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/46261/hero.webp 2400w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/cf8e6/hero.webp 7680w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/webp'>\n          <source srcset='/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/5a46d/hero.png 300w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/0a47e/hero.png 600w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/c1b63/hero.png 1200w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/d61c2/hero.png 1800w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/97a96/hero.png 2400w,\n/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/c841b/hero.png 7680w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/png'>\n          <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' src='/static/95612d1d27bec1fdf6eb365961742164/c1b63/hero.png' alt='Hero image of Visual Activities' title='' loading='lazy' decoding='async' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;'>\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"background\">Background</h2>\n<p>Lucid users often sought better ways to gather and visualize team feedback. The challenge was to create an on-canvas survey tool that allowed users to interact with digital shapes, facilitating a more engaging and intuitive decision-making process.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Time</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Tools</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Design team</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">12 months</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Figma</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Vishaka Nirmal</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Lucidchart</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Saurabh Phadnis</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Lucidspark</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Casey Robinson</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Maze</td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"concept\">Concept</h2>\n<p>The concept for Visual Activities originated from customer feedback, which emphasized the need for a more collaborative decision-making tool. We set out to explore how Lucid products could streamline this process, leading to the development of a visual survey tool that allowed each collaborator to manipulate shapes and provide input directly on the canvas.</p>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/32b38/concept.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 69%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset='/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/c85cb/concept.webp 300w,\n/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/e88ff/concept.webp 600w,\n/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/92f8c/concept.webp 1200w,\n/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/77e4e/concept.webp 1471w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/webp'>\n          <source srcset='/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/5a46d/concept.png 300w,\n/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/0a47e/concept.png 600w,\n/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/c1b63/concept.png 1200w,\n/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/32b38/concept.png 1471w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/png'>\n          <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' src='/static/88213b4748adf0a8653ad31162917a0c/c1b63/concept.png' alt='Early concept mocks' title='' loading='lazy' decoding='async' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;'>\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"research\">Research</h2>\n<p>Initial user research revealed that teams needed more flexible ways to make decisions collaboratively. To address this, I led design jams with UX designers across different teams and conducted early usability tests with 20 participants through UserTesting.com. These sessions provided valuable insights into how users interacted with the Figma prototypes and helped refine the tool's direction.</p>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/59058/research.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 85%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset='/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/c85cb/research.webp 300w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/e88ff/research.webp 600w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/92f8c/research.webp 1200w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/62ed8/research.webp 1800w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/57b3a/research.webp 2376w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/webp'>\n          <source srcset='/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/5a46d/research.png 300w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/0a47e/research.png 600w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/c1b63/research.png 1200w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/d61c2/research.png 1800w,\n/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/59058/research.png 2376w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/png'>\n          <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' src='/static/e3e02352ef9c561c15303fd48f725473/c1b63/research.png' alt='Research and early sketches' title='' loading='lazy' decoding='async' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;'>\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"strategy\">Strategy</h2>\n<p>With the concept validated, I led discussions with product managers and engineering teams to align our vision and secure investment in the Visual Activities feature. We outlined a strategic roadmap, focusing on creating a shape-like experience that felt both familiar and innovative for users.</p>\n<h2 id=\"iteration\">Iteration</h2>\n<p>Breaking traditional paradigms, we designed a freeform, shape-based survey experience. I iterated on the design, focusing on creating a seamless user experience that allowed for both participation and result visualization in a way that felt intuitive and engaging.</p>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/764d7/earlydesign.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 85%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset='/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/c85cb/earlydesign.webp 300w,\n/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/e88ff/earlydesign.webp 600w,\n/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/92f8c/earlydesign.webp 1200w,\n/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/63e37/earlydesign.webp 1782w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/webp'>\n          <source srcset='/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/5a46d/earlydesign.png 300w,\n/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/0a47e/earlydesign.png 600w,\n/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/c1b63/earlydesign.png 1200w,\n/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/764d7/earlydesign.png 1782w' sizes='(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px' type='image/png'>\n          <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' src='/static/d8eec193e7685f2b941ddd736af2c90d/c1b63/earlydesign.png' alt='Design iterations' title='' loading='lazy' decoding='async' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;'>\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"final-designs\">Final Designs</h2>\n<p>The final design features an on-canvas activity shape with two states: an 'edit mode' for setup and a 'participation mode' for user interaction. In edit mode, users can drag content into the shape, preparing it for participant interaction. Once editing is complete, the shape transforms, inviting collaborators to engage.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static/canvas-9465df8bfbdfa058e555b58c0eaead2f.gif\" alt=\"On-canvas shape functionality\"></p>\n<p>Participants enter their own mini-canvas, where they interact with the shapes to provide their responses. The design ensures clarity, with participants always aware of their active participation through visual cues like avatars and responsive objects.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static/participation-045a0563f7534e83bda5538eae6f6980.gif\" alt=\"Participation experience\"></p>\n<p>The results visualization showcases each participant's input in relation to the group's average response. This interactive data visualization allows teams to quickly understand consensus or divergence in opinions, enhancing the decision-making process.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static/results-d8cc3513b8f7faa75f4446c58bad86a4.gif\" alt=\"Results visualization\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"outcomes\">Outcomes</h2>\n<p>Visual Activities launched to all Lucid users in May 2023 and quickly gained traction as a powerful tool for collaborative decision-making. The iterative design process proved invaluable, allowing us to refine ideas rapidly and deliver a feature that meets user needs effectively. The success of Visual Activities showcases the potential for innovative, user-driven design in enhancing digital collaboration.</p>\n<p>I had the opportunity to present use cases for this tool alongside my team during one of Lucid's webinars. <a href=\"https://lucid.co/resources/webinars/use-cases-for-visual-activities-jan-2024\">Watch the presentation here!</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Visual Activities","isPasswordProtected":true,"password":"green","blockquoteColor":"#3C41C2"},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#lucid-softwares-visual-activities\">Lucid Software's Visual Activities</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#background\">Background</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#concept\">Concept</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#research\">Research</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#strategy\">Strategy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#iteration\">Iteration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#final-designs\">Final Designs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#outcomes\">Outcomes</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/visualactivities/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}